J/A+A/653/A41       L 98-59 (TOI-175) ESPRESSO observations   (Demangeon+, 2021)
================================================================================
Warm terrestrial planet with half the mass of Venus transiting a nearby star.
    Demangeon O.D.S., Zapatero Osorio M.R., Alibert Y., Barros S.C.C.,
